data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, single story home in Visalia! entry to tile and carpet flooring, an inviting fireplace in the family room, and lots of natural light. The kitchen offers elegant, light wood cabinetry. The primary bedroom features a large closet and a walk-in shower in the primary bathroom. Additional property highlights include ceiling fans, a laundry closet and a 2 car garage. Convenient to nearby schools, parks, and major freeways!
